text: Sergey Saychik (26 February 1957 - 5 October 2000) was a Soviet ski jumper. He competed in the normal hill and large hill events at the 1976 Winter Olympics. ==References== Category:1957 births Category:2000 deaths Category:Soviet male ski jumpers Category:Olympic ski jumpers of the Soviet Union Category:Ski jumpers at the 1976 Winter Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Perm
